videos.description: California QB Chase Garbers finds Trevon Clark wide open in the corner of the end zone for a 6-yard touchdown vs. Ole Miss.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Cal strikes first with wide-open TD) 2019/9/21

videos.headline: Cal strikes first with wide-open TD

videos.description: QB Matt Corral first connects with Octavious Cooley who dives at the pylon, but is called down at the 2-yard line. A few plays later, Corral is able to walk it in himself for a TD.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Ole Miss QB keeps it himself for TD) 2019/9/21

videos.headline: Ole Miss QB keeps it himself for TD

videos.description: Chase Garbers throws a nice pass to Christopher Brown Jr. who takes just a few steps into the end zone for a 13-yard Cal TD.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Cal's Brown hops into the end zone for 13-yard score) 2019/9/21

videos.headline: Cal's Brown hops into the end zone for 13-yard score

videos.description: Deantre Prince leaps in front of Cal TE Gavin Reinwald to intercept QB Chase Garbers' pass and returns it 21 yards, earning himself the Landshark turnover chain.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Prince dons Landshark chain after intercepting Cal's Garbers) 2019/9/21

videos.headline: Prince dons Landshark chain after intercepting Cal's Garbers

videos.description: Chase Garbers fires a pass to Jordan Duncan for a 9-yard touchdown in the third quarter vs. Ole Miss.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Duncan stays inbounds for Cal TD) 2019/9/21

videos.headline: Duncan stays inbounds for Cal TD

videos.description: Cal QB Chase Garbers throws his fourth touchdown pass on the day, setting up Jake Tonges for a 60-yard strike vs. Ole Miss.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Garbers' 4th TD pass is a 60-yard score) 2019/9/21

videos.headline: Garbers' 4th TD pass is a 60-yard score

videos.description: Playing his first career snap for Ole Miss, QB John Rhys Plumlee takes off for a 47-yard gain. On on the very next play, another true freshman, Jerrion Ealy runs for a 15-yard score.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Plumlee rips off 47-yard run, sets up TD on first collegiate drive) 2019/9/21

videos.headline: Plumlee rips off 47-yard run, sets up TD on first collegiate drive

videos.description: In the final minute of action with Ole Miss down a score, true freshman John Rhys Plumlee fires a deep pass to Demarcus Gregory for a 41-yard gain and a 1st down.
